{"tid":1393364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千其唔好中計！612基金要繼續支持","createTime":"2019-08-01T05:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:30:55.000Z","uid":191275,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c7de3681c6ab25b8a5ffc7bcb3c6c874f8e59c03","tid":1393364,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"最近見到好多所謂「可靠消息」嘅post<br />\n話612基金戶口有問題叫人唔好捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問咗係銀行做compliance多年嘅朋友仔，<br />\n佢表示d內容相當多疑點！<br />\n應該係唔想我地再捐錢幫義士<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原因: <br />\n1）金管局嘅責任唔係調查戶口，<br />\n負責調查戶口嘅係警察，<br />\n金管局只係收到投訴時叫銀行提供資料<br />\n<br />\n2）<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果警察想銀行凍結個戶口，<br />\n佢地要有實際証據去証明戶口嘅錢係用黎支持暴動，</span></strong><br />\n但呢樣好難証明到<br />\n(<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">612基金已經表明係唔會買防具/贊助小朋友買嘢食等</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢哋係支援被捕 / 受傷/ 情緒困擾嘅人)<br />\n<br />\n基金絕對唔係支持暴動 唔會有事！<br />\n<br />\n3）銀行當然有權以風險為理由取消612嘅戶口，<br />\n但做hsbc嘅朋友仔話唔覺得公司會咁做，<br />\n亦到收唔到任何風公司有咁嘅打算<br />\n(如果係中資銀行就危險d)<br />\n<br />\n4）如果大家有任何擔憂，<br />\n建議用現金存入戶口嘅方式捐錢，<br />\n咁就咩record都無 (雖然每日只可以收10萬)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RHxav8D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRHxav8D.png&h=79bd14c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基金其實點樣都會唔夠錢<br />\n大家千祈唔好停止捐款<br />\n唔好中計<br />\n義士唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要繼續支持 俾多人知<br />\n記住要fact check!!!!!"},{"pid":"b6604ced769b6890537e33b554f75344b69ebd22","tid":1393364,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:21:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c66245ddebe11d4415674090eb5f92a8a1069eb","tid":1393364,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"我要罷工！"},{"pid":"fce93feef902b54d74874174000c21a1db58e208","tid":1393364,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jX5bZ3F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjX5bZ3F.png&h=f70a4279&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cd318ab7cd6483f4033df77a75db85c31c44e39","tid":1393364,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:22:50.000Z","msg":"fact check重要！"},{"pid":"28019240bf8a0fc51ed3189000b51b9aa959ae37","tid":1393364,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"要支持義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c583892c09e2a37cfaa7738cd82a4a06b5de82ec","tid":1393364,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"749e997e611b7a71b181b47edee111aa6554353e","tid":1393364,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T0